      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Open race but happy to stick with FIELDS OF COURAGE (3) who broke through for an overdue win here last time and beat some of these. Meets them worst at the weights but hard to knock recent form and can go close again. HENNESSY LAD (1) ran a much-improved race second-up and is a third-up winner. Ready to win and shapes as one of the key chances. BEAU FACTOR (4) was placed behind FIELDS OF COURAGE last time in third. Meets the winner better at the weights and is one of the chief contenders. TENNESSEE WHISKEY (2) was the horse that split that pair and is also better off at the weights so has to be right in the mix. HE'S MAVERICK (7) ran a better race last time and is worth including.",
